high_descs: Walk through the kitchen over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the golden metal spoon with a blue handle up off of the counter in front of the sink.
Turn left, walk towards the kitchen counter, then hang a left and begin walking across the room, stop when at the glass bowl on the kitchen island and turn left to face the island.
Place the golden spoon handle up in the glass bowl that is on the kitchen island
Pick up the glass bowl with the golden spoon in it.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the glass bowl with the golden spoon in it into the right side of the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass bowl with a golden spoon into the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Move to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the sink.
Bring the spoon to the island.
Put the spoon in the bowl on the island.
Pick up the bowl from the island.
Bring the bowl to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Head straight to the kitchen sink
Pick up the serving spoon with the blue handle that is next to the dinner knife by the sink
Turn left and move forward towards the kitchen table
Place the blue serving spoon in the empty bowl on top of the table
Pickup the bowl with the blue serving spoon in it
Turn left and go to the kitchen sink
Place the bowl with blue spoon inside the sink
anns.task_desc: Moving a serving spoon in a bowl to the kitchen sink
